    • Class Model.CinemaMovie

      class CinemaMovie extends Object implements Serializable

      • Serialized Fields

        • endDate
          String endDate
          The date at which the cinema movie will be de-listed and unavailable for booking. Format of the date is in DD-MMM-YYYY (Eg: 31-Jan-2023 )
        • movie
          Movie movie
          The movie that has be registered as a cinema movie.
        • overallRating
          float overallRating
          The average of all the individual ratings given to the cinema movie by Movie-goers. Value of overall rating is to 1 decimal place. Overall rating will only be displayed if there are more than one individual rating. Else, "NA" will be displayed.
        • reviews
          List<Review> reviews
          A list of Review objects. Each Review corresponds to a review that a Movie-goer has given to the movie.
        • showTimes
          List<ShowTime> showTimes
          A list of ShowTime objects. Each ShowTime corresponds to a particular location, date and time that the cinema movie will be screened at.
        • status
          CinemaMovie.Status status
          Showing status of the cinema movie.
        • ticketSales
          double ticketSales
          The total amount of sales generated from ticket selling across all cineplexes.
        • type
          CinemaMovie.Type type
          Type of the cinema movie.

    • Class Model.ShowTime

      class ShowTime extends Object implements Serializable

      • Serialized Fields

        • cinemaCode
          String cinemaCode
          The code of the cinema which the cinema movie will be screened. Can only take the values of R0, R1, R2 or P3.
        • cineplexName
          String cineplexName
          The name of the cineplex which the cinema movie will be screened.
        • date
          String date
          The date at which the cinema movie will be screened. Format is DD-MMM-YYYY (Eg: 31-Jan-2023)
        • endTime
          String endTime
          The time at which the cinema movie will stop screening. Format is military time (Eg: 1600, 0400).
        • layout
          SeatLayout layout
          SeatLayout contains info about available seats for a show time. One SeatLayout for each show time.
        • startTime
          String startTime
          The time at which the cinema movie will start screening. Format is military time (Eg: 1600, 0400).
